data.description: Move-in ready Southside 2 story with new paint, new flooring, and new carpet throughout! Be invited into this home with a spacious living room including large windows for plenty of natural light. Tucked away is the oversized kitchen and dining area, complete with a new single stall sink, a large pantry, laundry room, and storage closet. Bedroom and bath on the main level offers privacy in its own corner of the home. New vanity and flooring installed in the full bath on the main level. Upstairs boasts a large guest bedroom. Main bedroom upstairs with spacious walk-in closet and close access to the full bath with brand new double vanities! Xeriscaped front and back yards with a small patch of lawn in the back! Solar panels for minimal electric bills, a tankless water heater, central air and updated plumbing! Smart garage door that integrates with Amazon and doorbell camera all transfer with the property! Home sits in quiet neighborhood complete with access to playgrounds, parks, and walking trails just steps away!
